song.title: Music for Nerds
song.info:
Throw your hands in the air if you're just like me, really good with your hands on the EDB.
We make music. We make music.
You can call us geeks, you can call us nerds, the music is the shit for the dancing herds.
We make music. We make muic.
--
3rd @ Solskogen 2016 Newskool Music Compo.
